* SCD Type 2\nTable Design
** Required Columns
***_ Surrogate key (IDENTITY)
***_ Natural/business key
***_ Business attributes
***_ valid_from TIMESTAMP
***_ valid_to TIMESTAMP
***_ is_current BOOLEAN
** Delta Features
***_ GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY
***_ enableChangeDataFeed = true
** Valid To Convention
***_ Current row: 9999-12-31
***_ Expired row: actual end date
@endmindmap
